cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.SI 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for extracting hypernymy relationships. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of embeddings, which suggests that it could also be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves unsupervised learning techniques, which could place it under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which could place it under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves the use of sense-aware relationships, which could place it under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
